## ðŸ”¹ Roadmap  

### Phase 1: Foundation (Completed)  
- Deployment of BQN on the TON blockchain  
- Fixed total supply set to 100,000 BQN  
- Minting and burning permanently disabled  
- Token metadata finalized  
- Logo prepared and optimized (100 KB)  
- GitHub repository created  
- Initial liquidity pool launched  

### Phase 2: Stability & Transparency (In Progress)  
- Maintain a single primary liquidity pool  
- Avoid liquidity fragmentation across multiple pools  
- Monitor price behavior and market dynamics  
- Ensure full transparency in documentation  

### Phase 3: Verification  
- Submit Pull Request to Tonkeeper assets repository  
- Metadata and asset review  
- Achieve Verified Token status in Tonkeeper  

### Phase 4: Value Maturity  
- Preserve long-term scarcity  
- Support organic trading only  
- Improve branding and documentation  
- Optional non-inflationary integrations  

### Phase 5: Long-Term Sustainability  
- Full decentralization  
- Community-driven transparency  
- Position BQN as a long-term digital asset  

---

## ðŸ”¹ Strategy  

- No supply expansion under any condition  
- Price determined purely by market demand  
- Liquidity managed carefully to reduce volatility  
- Long-term vision over short-term speculation  

